* {{Cite news | last1 = Powell |first1=Steve John|last2= Cabello| first2 = Angeles Marin | title = Japan's Mountain Ascetic Hermits | newspaper = [[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] | date = May 12, 2021 | url = http://www.bbc.com/travel/story/20210511-japans-mountain-ascetic-hermits}}

